{"tid":2404001,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【愛情】【短】講咗十幾次，我條女都仲問緊我咩係越位","createTime":"2021-02-11T12:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T17:27:07.000Z","uid":255045,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0da1fb170af1ae4a934fd9d817fee0fca84069","tid":2404001,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:24:00.000Z","msg":"嚟到每月小說計劃嘅第三個月，今次為大家帶嚟一篇輕鬆啲嘅短篇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JszkMQf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJszkMQf.gif&h=0dbd0040&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sw35XXr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSw35XXr.gif&h=1737119f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（鍾意我幅gif嘅話，可以去今個月畫嘢post到留名，睇吓會唔會畫中你個名）<br />\n<br />\n故事簡介：<br />\n「多義性」係後現代文學嘅特徵之一，最顯見嘅就係詞語嘅多義性。<br />\n喺今個月嘅依篇短篇小說入面，「越位」有著唔同方面嘅解讀。愛情、社會發展、小朋友上堂⋯⋯原來除咗足球，越位嘅界線喺生活上面都可能難以劃界。原因可能出自本身：本來位置依樣嘢就係難以定義。喺無常多變嘅世界之中，有咩等緊Randol、阿P同埋Doria三個人呢？<br />\n<br />\n導讀問題：<br />\n1. 「多義性」係後現代文學嘅特徵之一，最顯見嘅就係詞語嘅多義性。喺依篇小說入面，「越位」一詞有著多重意義：喺愛情關係入面，喺足球入面，喺小朋友行為方面⋯⋯越位有著點樣嘅唔同意思呢？<br />\n2. 越位關乎「位置」。當講起位置嗰陣，你會諗起固定嘅位置，定係可以移動嘅位置呢？位置係咪指一定要固定嘅地方？咁我哋依家又喺咩位置呢？<br />\n<br />\n1. 越位位置<br />\n對上一次最近嘅足球賽事係咩啊？<br />\n<br />\n吓，即係幾個聯賽原來會同時搞㗎？<br />\n<br />\n咁喺幾時搞㗎？<br />\n<br />\n即係全年都有㗎？<br />\n<br />\n點解之前啲人要通宵睇波嘅？<br />\n<br />\n乜原來每個星期都有通宵波㗎？<br />\n<br />\n咁依家有咩邊隊打緊啊？<br />\n<br />\n曼聯個聯盟入面係有幾多隊球隊㗎？<br />\n<br />\n這些問題全都是由Doria說出口，聽落奇怪，但從她的角度來說聽起來也合理。"},{"pid":"870277c675d8008b763255117681dffa89213954","tid":2404001,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"我今年打算每個月出一篇短篇小說，仲有畫名post，鍾意嘅可以追蹤我<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以嘅話留個comment，已經係好大鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇翻之前嘅小說同畫名post，可以去返下邊嘅links<br />\n啲畫嘢post已經截晒名，但想睇下我其他嘅畫都可以click入去睇下<br />\n<br />\n2020年1月 主題：未來<br />\n【都市奇幻】【短】《預留未來》<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gxHPdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gxHPdS</a> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8wWGwi7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8wWGwi7.gif&h=bfa9595b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男主角執執下屋唔見咗個老婆、又撞翻中學女神&mdash;&mdash;睇完都係唔知噏乜春&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n畫嘢post：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/md6CO6k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmd6CO6k.jpg&h=ab764ef0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKJmwj9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKJmwj9.gif&h=90dae849&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5eVHfMV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5eVHfMV.gif&h=df651b64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新一年，一人一個想未來仲保留得著嘅嘢 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gzysaS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gzysaS</a> <br />\n<br />\n2020年12月 主題：恐懼<br />\n故事：<br />\n【懸疑】【短】《異常接近！》<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gruuAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gruuAS</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6pLv84F.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6pLv84F.gif&h=1179bcaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事簡介：懸疑故。有個fd 失咗蹤：有伊藤潤二、村上春樹、UFO同蛇&mdash;&mdash;睇完唔知噏乜春系列&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n畫嘢post：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o64H0bV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo64H0bV.jpg&h=dae0997f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n試下畫名 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aGBaBRU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aGBaBRU</a><br />\n<br />\n[🚅特急小說] <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GOOqdzd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOOqdzd.jpg&h=7f4c4bc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全民植樹 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gvRrwS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gvRrwS</a>"},{"pid":"4e2a52593e30df47b8f0f6e126ccc2e0991e2a3e","tid":2404001,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:37:27.000Z","msg":"Randol跟她拍拖三年，她仍然搞不清一些基礎的足球知識。<br />\n<br />\n有時她捱夜跟他一起看球賽時，她依舊會問他：<br />\n<br />\n「點解頭先個球證會吹嘅？」<br />\n<br />\n「點解喺越位啊？」<br />\n<br />\n「吓，咁其實咩係越位啊？」<br />\n<br />\n起初Randol還以為她說笑，只是在裝傻。<br />\n<br />\n記得2018年的萬聖節，她說想要扮成祖雲達斯，<br />\n<br />\n他才知道她真的是傻，不是扮出來的。<br />\n<br />\n「吓，乜原來祖雲達斯唔一個人嚟㗎？我點知喎。佢改到個名咁似人嘅。」"},{"pid":"a975b231fc00092d5aef310bae76351a2240cad3","tid":2404001,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc787e772ace07fdaaa2d7e8f59c5cb7840d1058","tid":2404001,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a975b231fc00092d5aef310bae76351a2240cad3","tid":2404001,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:53:48.000Z","msg":"yo 油巴～<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec43711858f5d7dd9d8aa6986bc2f15182dc072c","tid":2404001,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc787e772ace07fdaaa2d7e8f59c5cb7840d1058","tid":2404001,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a975b231fc00092d5aef310bae76351a2240cad3","tid":2404001,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:53:48.000Z","m