021-02-11T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T17:19:56.000Z","msg":"新年快樂 身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T17:22:15.000Z","msg":"新年快樂～<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lucky.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身體健康 龍馬精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b014fa45f1071b163a3cb283cf862847a9521844","tid":2404001,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T17:23:03.000Z","msg":"那是2018年的事。<br />\n<br />\n2019年的萬聖節，誰都沒有心情出去酒吧喝酒看球賽。<br />\n<br />\n兩口子在租來的屋中，看著Facebook上的新聞直播：<br />\n<br />\n藍旗，胡椒噴霧，和攀上燈柱、衣領打開、整塊臉都亮著熾熱紅光的男人。<br />\n<br />\n眼中帶著淚水。"},{"pid":"f125b979ba22058b3b7b1f047c62a08551d55fe6","tid":2404001,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T17:23:20.000Z","msg":"Doria本來是個愛早睡的人。<br />\n<br />\n白天已經要晨早流流回到學校，放學後也會處理Instagram專頁的事、整理來自教育界同工的投稿。<br />\n<br />\n然而，每當上晚有球賽，她仍然會陪在他身邊。<br />\n<br />\n偶爾看看電話； 在半場後的十分鐘，便會慣性地把頭放到他的前臂上，然後發出像貓般細微而低沉的呼嚕聲。<br />\n<br />\n一片綠野上，好幾個人追著一顆足球來來回回地跑。<br />\n<br />\n贏和輸，估計對她來說，並不如將怪獸家長的無理要求廣播出來和金剛Crew的足球影片有趣。<br />\n但她還是會在自己的身旁。這才是最重要的。"},{"pid":"6cb0f17a70872da7f472fe74ab80f524b32bfe05","tid":2404001,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T17:23:40.000Z","msg":"2019年後，球賽直播換上了新聞直播，<br />\n<br />\n她仍然在旁，在他極為憤怒時撫摸他的頭、撫摸他的前臂。<br />\n<br />\n把自己的手伸進他的掌裡。<br />\n<br />\n如同兩塊相鄰的拼圖，如同對準榫位的傢俬組件，<br />\n<br />\n合理而自然，註定相合。<br />\n<br />\n這時，Randol才發現原來這種相同比陪伴更為重要。<br />\n<br />\n在這裡，狹小的空間是廣乏普遍的存在。<br />\n<br />\n在一二百呎的單位中，情緒更易渲染。<br />\n<br />\n倆人看著搖晃鏡頭的畫面，<br />\n<br />\n不談未來，不談現在。<br />\n<br />\n沉默的共鳴勝過一切。"},{"pid":"38d32269dcc94b388da5db71b1a5b5bf34aa8f42","tid":2404001,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdf7aa011de0a80a267abc9a5dadd6cc023e880d","tid":2404001,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad4a7df47a12828d7a6ca3c4b29b2f7a567f2a4c","tid":2404001,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0d8f837c6f1be3dd4a2d23e1bd60c4f3ee41246","tid":2404001,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T17:19:56.000Z","msg":"新年快樂 身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T17:22:15.000Z","msg":"新年快樂～<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lucky.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身體健康 龍馬精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T17:27:07.000Z","msg":"心想事成 出入平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}